{
  "stem": "14552.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we had our growing-- the growing pains, and the survival, and, and the making-- keeping the family together.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We had a 12 o'clock lunch, midday dinner, where everybody in the family was there exactly on time.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "There was no such thing as, sorry, I'm late.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "That was the ritual of the family.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And we were very close.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And the store was closed from 12:00 to 2:00.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And we were around the table for that time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And then we went back to work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "The rest of the day was any which way you wanted to.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "You could eat anywhere you wanted.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "So we were very close.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And my mother, the pride she had in us was nice.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I remember-- now, I remember the face or expressions that she had when she would lean out the window and look at her children going to temple or going on a holiday, somebody dressed up.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a mother who was proud.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She had three boys, three girls.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What more could she ask?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Mhm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What-- I gather that you, you went to temple, so--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was only one kind I know of.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that was men were downstairs, and women were upstairs.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And for me, it was just natural to go sometimes to temple with my mother.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, we had--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had every holiday.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Every holiday was very carefully observed, with all the good food.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother was a very good cook.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was one of those cooks that the food was delicate and tasty.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There wasn't much of it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "No one overate.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was always enough for a beggar or two to have leftovers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But every food was-- the food there was good.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was fresh.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it well-made, delicately.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was nice food.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
